.  Nm vim Pa log
. Ed
.\" }}}
.\" exit {{{
.It Ic exit Op Li reboot No | Li poweroff
. Bd -literal
.  Nm smrt Cm detach
. Ed
. Pp
If you want to reboot or shutdown your refhosts use
. Li Nm smrt Cm run Nm reboot
or
. Li Nm smrt Cm run Nm poweroff
followed by
. Li Nm smrt Cm detach Fl \-dead Ns .
.\" }}}
